Description:

Overseas Manpower Corporation Limited issued a total of 470 vacancies for the posts of Staff Nurse & Others. The online application for these posts under OMCL shall start from 25.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 30.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Application fee:

The application fee for OMCL Staff Nurse Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 25.04.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 30.04.2021

Educational qualification:

You must have the diploma/degree in relevant field to apply for the post of Staff Nurse & Others.

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 22 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 35 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

OMCL Staff Nurse & Others Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Staff Nurse & Others is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed. 

How to apply for OMCL Staff Nurse Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of OMCL.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Staff Nurse & Others.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
